imdb.plot outline: A Tv series focused on making it in the Big Apple...working, hustling, and grinding to get ahead. It can be hard to find your way, to be somebody, or just to be happy in the Big Apple. Follow the lives of New Yorkers working hard to become a model, a nurse, an actress, a singer, and experience their highs, lows, hopes, disillusions, and successes. Living in New York Manhattan - Harlem - Brooklyn - Bronx without a script facing your own reality.
